Introduction

Yunju, formerly known as Seo Yunju, is a South Korean singer under Pocket7 Entertainment.

From 2019 to 2021, Yunju was a member of the pre-debut team "ISE" (known after debut as bugAboo) under A team Entertainment. Her departure from both the agency and the group was confirmed in July 2021.

On September 8, Yunju was revealed as a contestant on the MBC survival show "My Teenage Girl". She was eliminated during the second mid-point check in the fourth episode.

On September 1, 2022, Yunju was revealed as a member of the girl group MIMIIROSE under YES IM Entertainment. They debuted on September 16, 2022, with the single "AWESOME".

On November 21, 2023, MIMIIROSE's departure from YES IM Entertainment was announced, though the group was confirmed to not have disbanded and is in talks of signing with a new agency.

On March 26, 2024, it was announced that the members had signed an exclusive contract with Pocket7 Entertainment, continuing their activities as a group with the addition of two new members.
